scene derivative
claim "A derivative measures local change."
subject [[Derivative]]

state x = slider -5..5 default 1 label "x"
derive y = x * x
derive slope = 2 * x

mark curve parabola "y = x²" y "x*x" tone info
mark point current "Current point" x x y y tone success
mark tangent local "Local slope" at current slope slope tone warning

rule slope < 0 => note "The function is decreasing here."
rule slope > 0 => note "The function is increasing here."

layout chart x -5..5 y 0..25
